CREATE TABLE `spider2-public-data.goog_blockchain_tron_mainnet_us.blocks`
(
  block_hash STRING,
  block_number INT64,
  block_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  parent_hash STRING,
  size INT64,
  extra_data STRING,
  gas_limit INT64,
  gas_used INT64,
  base_fee_per_gas INT64,
  mix_hash STRING,
  nonce BIGNUMERIC,
  difficulty STRUCT<string_value STRING, bignumeric_value BIGNUMERIC>,
  total_difficulty STRUCT<string_value STRING, bignumeric_value BIGNUMERIC>,
  miner STRING,
  uncles_sha3 STRING,
  uncles ARRAY<STRING>,
  transactions_root STRING,
  receipts_root STRING,
  state_root STRING,
  logs_bloom STRING
);

CREATE TABLE `spider2-public-data.goog_blockchain_tron_mainnet_us.logs`
(
  block_hash STRING,
  block_number INT64,
  block_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  transaction_hash STRING,
  transaction_index INT64,
  log_index INT64,
  address STRING,
  data STRING,
  topics ARRAY<STRING>,
  removed BOOL
);
